org.apache.xmlbeans.impl.tool
Interface SchemaCompilerExtension

public interface SchemaCompilerExtension

This interface is implemented by Schema Compiler Extensions. By implementing this class you can then pass this class via the command line param extension to the SchemaCompiler class which will then in turn call this class back once the compilation is complete with the resulting SchemaTypeSystem.
